Query VIP customer list from database (table 1)
column3:
1. Login the system with Manager role.
2. Click [Search] button in the left side of home screen.
3. On [Query] dialog, select [VIP] in [Customer Type] combobox
4. Click  [Search] button
column4: 4. List with 10 VIP customers is displayed on [Query] dialog
column8: In database, table 1 [CustomerVIP] have more than 10 records
